data.description:
Lovely Ranch style home with 3 bedroom, 2 bath plus flex room located in Sage Creek. New LVP  flooring throughout the house makes it great for allergies and easy to clean. All appliances remain including refrigerator, washer, dryer an blinds. Split floor plan for privacy. Open floor plan for many decoration options.Kitchen has easy care, scratch resistant cabinets. Dining area, living room and flex room are open and spacious. Large owners suite with large master bathroom and walk-in closet. Owner's bathroom has dual sink, garden tub, shower and private toilet closet. Two additional bedrooms on the other side of the house share a comfortable bathroom and linen closet. Flex rom could be 4th bedroom, office formal dining room etc, many possibilities. 2 car garage with opener. Spacious laundry room has shelving. and enough space for separate freezer. There are sprinklers on all sides, and a storage building in the backyard. 
Sage Creek is less than a mile from I-20 with easy access to Augusta and Columbia, minutes away from USCA, hospital, downtown Aiken and restaurants and shopping. County taxes only. House qualifies for 100% USDA financing. This is a must see!
